{
  "id": "RAW_07d7b2",
  "title": "AI 故事随心绘：多主体 ID 保留，个性化生成",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTM5NTg2OA==&mid=2247503118&idx=2&sn=ae198b21dfd157638e7942315bfe2c8a&subscene=0",
  "date": "2025-05-07 08:01:00",
  "author": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
  "siteName": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <article data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"4EZlwoKE04YLlxAY\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-bottom: 3px;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 5px 18px;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n        <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n         <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">00</span></span>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-left: 18px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">前言</span></span>\n       </section>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">近期通义实验室提出了一种AnyStory的方法，旨在实现高质量的个性化文本到图像生成，支持单个和多个主体。</span></span></p>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-bottom: 3px;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 5px 18px;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n        <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n         <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></span>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-left: 18px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">在线体验</span></strong></span>\n       </section>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">小程序链接：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://modelscope.cn/studios/iic/AnyStory</span></span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <mp-common-miniprogram class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_miniprogram_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"insertminiprogram\" data-miniprogram-path=\"pages/Webview/index?realUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fmodelscope.cn%2Fstudios%2Fiic%2FAnyStory\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"魔搭社区ModelScope\" data-miniprogram-avatar=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/3guAKJVCsrErLIDjxCstLIWSGWzm6bkKmIPkwV4aibRa1stVPw8yXPNN4Tb7F9oO6OgeWULOCPr0fbGHQ1AyBvg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=200\" data-miniprogram-title=\"AI故事随心绘-AnyStory\" data-miniprogram-imageurl=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8ZLuyaibrZbm2tdMiaQzQ1VmLeQy31yIIjp5qrRv62EJkqHpQibhicdBOHFj9jicb2uXTKW5M3SqK5bicepbsK2Z4bVA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-miniprogram-type=\"card\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wx11f4f36712a16060\" data-miniprogram-imageurlback=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8ZLuyaibrZbm2tdMiaQzQ1VmLeQy31yIIjpDyfQT93C5xl5P4fPm6CjDs9rvYxCBrE2aY8w9jzic0aibmTLEc1iaPicA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\" data-miniprogram-cropperinfo=\"%7B%22c%22%3A%7B%22x%22%3A54%2C%22y%22%3A0%2C%22x2%22%3A222.75%2C%22y2%22%3A135%2C%22w%22%3A168.75%2C%22h%22%3A135%7D%7D\"></mp-common-miniprogram>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">该方法通过结合强大的通用图像编码器（如ReferenceNet）与CLIP视觉编码器来实现高保真度的主题特征编码，并利用一个解耦的实例感知主题路由器来精确预测并引导主题条件的注入，从而实现了灵活且可控的个性化生成。实验结果表明，该方法在保持主题细节、文本描述一致性以及多主题个性化方面表现出色。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，AnyStory还展示了任何故事框架的潜力，不仅限于人脸或特定类别物体的个性化，而且能够处理更广泛的主题，包括非人类实体和复杂背景下的场景生成。尽管存在一些限制，如无法为图像生成定制背景，但研究团队展望未来的研究方向，包括扩展对背景控制的能力和进一步减少复制粘贴效应，以提升生成图像的质量。</span></span></p>\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"126504\">\n    <section>\n     <section>\n      <section data-autoskip=\"1\">\n       <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100018080\" data-ratio=\"0.7712962962962963\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6f73413b-4307-4c6a-b65d-d1911ab25300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: 525px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 681px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6f73413b-4307-4c6a-b65d-d1911ab25300/public\">\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><span leaf=\"\">课代表划重点</span></span></strong></p>\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"126504\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 15px 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(84, 160, 247);visibility: visible;\">\n      <section data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75;\">\n       <ol style=\"width: 577.422px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n        <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AnyStory提出了一种增强的主题表示编码器和解耦的实例感知路由模块，用于实现灵活可控的个性化图像生成。</span></p></li>\n        <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">相较于现有方法，AnyStory能够更准确地感知并预测主题的潜在条件区域，从而提高生成效果。</span></p></li>\n        <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AnyStory采用了CLIP视觉编码器和轻量级ReferenceNet来高保真度地对一般主题进行细节编码。</span></p></li>\n        <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">解耦的实例感知路由模块可以适应单或多主题的个性化生成需求。</span></p></li>\n        <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n         <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AnyStory通过使用路由主题的方法实现了一致性和多样性的平衡，并且不需要预先定义布局掩模。</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-indent: 0em;font-size: 14px;\"></span></p></li>\n       </ol>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n    <section style=\"padding-bottom: 3px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n      <section style=\"padding: 5px 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n        <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n         <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></span>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"padding-left: 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">模型结构</span></strong></span>\n       </section>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100018073\" data-ratio=\"0.4740740740740741\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/63c14910-0382-4504-ad6e-26df250dd500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:616px;height:292px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/63c14910-0382-4504-ad6e-26df250dd500/public\">\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AnyStory遵循“encode-then-route”的传统条件生成范式，首先利用简化的ReferenceNet 结合 CLIP视觉编码器结合subject编码，然后采用解耦的instance-aware subject router来引导subject条件注入，训练过程分为2个阶段，subject Encoder训练阶段和Router训练阶段，为了简单起见，图中省略了文本分支。</span></span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><span leaf=\"\">模型效果：</span></span></strong></h3>\n   <table>\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td data-colwidth=\"557\" width=\"557\" valign=\"middle\" align=\"center\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">单实体生成</span></span></td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td data-colwidth=\"557\" width=\"557\" valign=\"middle\" align=\"center\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\">\n       <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100018081\" data-ratio=\"1.2724719101123596\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4aa300b-0654-4b97-a74a-2805fba43200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"356\" style=\"height: 226.5px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 178px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4aa300b-0654-4b97-a74a-2805fba43200/public\">\n       </section></td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <table>\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td data-colwidth=\"557\" width=\"557\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">卡通风格。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一只羊脚踩滑板在城市里滑翔，手里拿着一块木牌，上面写着\"TongYi\"</span></span></td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td data-colwidth=\"557\" width=\"557\" valign=\"middle\" align=\"center\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\">\n       <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100018082\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8166724d-9ff7-4c22-096d-08acabdf9900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"512\" style=\"height: 256px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 256px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8166724d-9ff7-4c22-096d-08acabdf9900/public\">\n       </section></td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n   <table>\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td data-colwidth=\"258\" width=\"258\" valign=\"middle\" align=\"center\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\">\n       <section>\n        <span leaf=\"\">原图</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n       </section></td>\n      <td data-colwidth=\"258\" width=\"258\" valign=\"middle\" align=\"left\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">卡通风格。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">孙悟空站在一辆坦克上，高举一块古朴木牌，木牌上写着'AnyStory'。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">背景是赛博朋克风格高楼林立的城市天空。</span></span></td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td data-colwidth=\"258\" width=\"258\" valign=\"middle\" align=\"center\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\">\n       <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100018083\" data-ratio=\"1.17\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c9ff69aa-ebf5-4ff6-cbac-4d2425de6d00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"height: 241px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 206px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c9ff69aa-ebf5-4ff6-cbac-4d2425de6d00/public\">\n       </section><span style=\"display: none;line-height: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">‍</span></span></td>\n      <td data-colwidth=\"258\" width=\"258\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\">\n       <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d53388a6-fb2f-4274-939d-69a587c22100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"512\" style=\"height: 256px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 256px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100018084\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d53388a6-fb2f-4274-939d-69a587c22100/public\">\n       </section></td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <table>\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"2\" data-colwidth=\"268,268\" valign=\"bottom\" align=\"center\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\">\n       <h4><span leaf=\"\">多实体生成</span></h4></td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td data-colwidth=\"268\" width=\"268\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\">\n       <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100018085\" data-ratio=\"0.9538152610441767\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c175c5aa-6c5e-4373-eff0-d1d26de69200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"996\" style=\"height: 270px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 283px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c175c5aa-6c5e-4373-eff0-d1d26de69200/public\">\n       </section></td>\n      <td data-colwidth=\"268\" width=\"268\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\">\n       <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4aba7d9-7532-4724-f308-090b6a4d8e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"470\" style=\"height: 235px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 235px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100018086\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4aba7d9-7532-4724-f308-090b6a4d8e00/public\">\n       </section></td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"2\" data-colwidth=\"268,268\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">两个男人坐在一张木桌旁，桌上摆满了美味的食物和一壶酒。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">其中一个男人手持酒杯，仰头畅饮，神情豪迈；</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">另一个男人则微笑着为他斟酒，两人谈笑风生。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">背景是一座古朴的凉亭，周围环绕着翠绿的竹林，阳光透过竹叶洒下斑驳的光影。</span></span></td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"2\" data-colwidth=\"268,268\" valign=\"bottom\" align=\"center\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\">\n       <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100018089\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1c17d41f-68c8-4d5a-f554-1f0a0ecf0c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"512\" style=\"height: 256px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 256px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1c17d41f-68c8-4d5a-f554-1f0a0ecf0c00/public\">\n       </section></td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">点击</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">阅读原文，</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">即可跳转体验~</span></span></p><pre style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;overflow:auto;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14.875px;font-family:SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><article data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"QvjnAAAeRzJynXo5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><article data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"QvjnAA9pBXJbnXo5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"></span></section></section></section></article></article></pre>\n  </article>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"10000\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "AnyStory 是一种支持多主体 ID 保留和个性化生成的高质量文本到图像生成方法。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "AnyStory 是一种支持多主体 ID 保留和个性化生成的高质量文本到图像生成方法。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了通义实验室提出的 AnyStory 方法，该方法旨在实现高质量的个性化文本到图像生成，尤其擅长处理多主体场景，实现不同主体的身份一致性。AnyStory 结合了强大的通用图像编码器（如 ReferenceNet）与 CLIP 视觉编码器，以实现高保真度的主题特征编码，并利用解耦的实例感知主题路由器来精确预测和引导主题条件的注入，从而实现灵活且可控的个性化生成。实验结果表明，该方法在保持主题细节、文本描述一致性以及多主题个性化方面表现出色。该方法不仅限于人脸或特定类别物体的个性化，而且能够处理更广泛的主题，包括非人类实体和复杂背景下的场景生成。AnyStory 可应用于个性化内容创作、虚拟形象设计等领域。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AnyStory 通过增强的主题表示编码器和解耦的实例感知路由模块，实现了高质量的个性化图像生成，尤其擅长多主体场景。",
      "explanation": "通过结合 ReferenceNet 和 CLIP 视觉编码器，AnyStory 能够生成具有高保真度主题特征的图像。"
    },
    {
      "point": "解耦的实例感知主题路由器实现了灵活且可控的生成。",
      "explanation": "该模块能够精确预测并引导主题条件的注入，从而支持单主体和多主体的个性化生成。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AnyStory 在主题细节保持和文本描述一致性方面表现出色。",
      "explanation": "实验结果表明，AnyStory 能够生成与文本描述高度一致，并保持主题细节的图像。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AnyStory 通过路由主题的方法，在生成图像的一致性和多样性之间取得了平衡。",
      "explanation": "AnyStory 在生成图像时，既能保证主题的一致性，又能生成多样化的内容。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AnyStory 提出了一种增强的主题表示编码器和解耦的实例感知路由模块，用于实现灵活可控的个性化图像生成。",
    "相较于现有方法，AnyStory 能够更准确地感知并预测主题的潜在条件区域，从而提高生成效果。",
    "AnyStory 采用了 CLIP 视觉编码器和轻量级 ReferenceNet 来高保真度地对一般主题进行细节编码。"
  ],
